          Media queries
          <br/><br/>
          Add the
          <a class="link" href="https://github.com/scottjehl/Respond" class="link" >respond.js</a>
          polyfill to support media queries.
    tr.table__row
      td.table__row__item
        .table__row__item__content up to IE 8
      td.table__row__item
        .table__row__item__content.
          CSS 3 pseudo element selectors (::selector)
          <br/><br/>
          Replace every double colon selector (::selector)
          with a single colon one (:selector).
          <br/><br/>
          We recommend to use
          <a class="link" href="https://www.npmjs.com/package/postcss-pseudoelements" >postcss-pseudoelements</a>
          postcss plugin to automate this task.
